text: BauNetz Media is a German online platform offering services for architects, planners, and designers. The online magazine BauNetz is dedicated to daily news in international architecture. The magazine was started in 1996 and is located at Berlin Charlottenburg. BauNetz Media is part of the Paris-based group Infopro Digital. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Architecture magazines Category:Architecture websites Category:Visual arts magazines published in Germany Category:Magazines established in 1996 Category:Magazines published in Berlin Category:Online magazines Category:1996 establishments in Germany Category:German-language magazines
